ement at the university conferring it. All I have is my Cantab BA 1922, and that suffices. I know that many people, such as politicians, actors, foreign writers etc., do not apply this principle but I have been sticking to it for years and would be unable to renounce it now, even in the case of your offer, a particularly tempting one for me.

I entreat you to understand and excuse me.





Very cordially,

Vladimir Nabokov





TO: DAN LACY1

TL (XEROX), 2 pp.





